overview.en: STARFISH Exchange is a cryptocurrency trading platform. At present, the number of users of STARFISH Exchange has reached several millions. Through user experience and satisfaction degree survey, it has received 99% users’ recognition, which is the core competitiveness of STARFISH Exchange.
overview.zh: STARFISH交易所是一个加密货币交易平台。 目前，STARFISH交易所的用户数已达数百万。 通过用户体验和满意度调查，它已经获得了99％的用户认可，这是STARFISH Exchange的核心竞争力。
